  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Little Rooms! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217260/extras/01623e4a56d59a525919bbc33b5a1beb.avif?t=1727781554\" width=600 height=142 /></span>Enter a house, pick a room and search the requested objects!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take your time, play cool, enjoy :) </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Six very different houses </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Visit bedrooms, kitchens, gardens, reading rooms and more! </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Four different game modes:</strong>   <br>- Search: Found a very specific object 3 times. <br>- Collection: Find a list of objects around the room. <br>- Riddle: One cryptic description to find a special object. <br>- Night Shift: Capture the little phantoms with your torchlight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extra features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Jukebox: control the music and discover our homemade playlist.<br>- Weather system: you decide the mood of the scene :)<br>- You unlocked all the rooms in the house? Unlock a special game mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have suggestions, feedback or just want to say hi, check the Discussions:<br></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217260/extras/9f99cbf7f2a31f9fac615e5f0c8c3fff.avif?t=1727781554\" width=600 height=219 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Little Rooms! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217260/extras/01623e4a56d59a525919bbc33b5a1beb.avif?t=1727781554\" width=600 height=142 /></span>Enter a house, pick a room and search the requested objects!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take your time, play cool, enjoy :) </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Six very different houses </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Visit bedrooms, kitchens, gardens, reading rooms and more! </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Four different game modes:</strong>   <br>- Search: Found a very specific object 3 times. <br>- Collection: Find a list of objects around the room. <br>- Riddle: One cryptic description to find a special object. <br>- Night Shift: Capture the little phantoms with your torchlight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extra features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Jukebox: control the music and discover our homemade playlist.<br>- Weather system: you decide the mood of the scene :)<br>- You unlocked all the rooms in the house? Unlock a special game mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have suggestions, feedback or just want to say hi, check the Discussions:<br></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217260/extras/9f99cbf7f2a31f9fac615e5f0c8c3fff.avif?t=1727781554\" width=600 height=219 /></span></p>",
